# How to do

### Gerar um thumbnail

Para consumir o endpoint principal de **geração de thumbnail**, basta executar:
```shell
curl --request POST \
  --url http://localhost:8080/api/users/eea0b8ba-b195-4e08-8a30-1df60854186e/thumbnails/create \
  --header 'Content-Type: application/json' \
  --data '{
	"id": "eea0b8ba-b195-4e08-8a30-1df60854186e",
	"fileName": "rponte.png",
	"photo": ""
}'
```
